GetClassType.name: GetClassType
GetClassType.description: Returns a type of the ApiContentControlListEntry class.

GetParent.name: GetParent
GetParent.description: Returns the parent of a content control list item in the collection of list items.

Select.name: Select
Select.description: Selects the list entry in a drop-down list or combo box content control and sets the text of the content control to the value of the item.

MoveUp.name: MoveUp
MoveUp.description: Moves the current item in the parent drop-down list or combo box content control up one element.

MoveDown.name: MoveDown
MoveDown.description: Moves an item in a drop-down list or combo box content control down one item, so that it is after the item that originally followed it.

GetIndex.name: GetIndex
GetIndex.description: Returns the index of a content control list item in the collection of list items.

SetIndex.name: SetIndex
SetIndex.description: Sets the index of a content control list item in the collection of list items.

Delete.name: Delete
Delete.description: Deletes the specified item in a combo box or drop-down list content control..

GetText.name: GetText
GetText.description: Returns a String that represents the display text of a list item for a drop-down list or combo box content control.

SetText.name: SetText
SetText.description: Sets a String that represents the display text of a list item for a drop-down list or combo box content control.

GetValue.name: GetValue
GetValue.description: Returns a String that represents the value of a list item for a drop-down list or combo box content control.

SetValue.name: SetValue
SetValue.description: Sets a String that represents the value of a list item for a drop-down list or combo box content control.
